!! Introduction
In the series of dating, the concept of boy friend and girl friend has been suspiciously absent.
Each in your own groups came up with your own definition of love.

!!! Love Defined
Love is a decision to joyfully commit ourselves to the good of another, regardless of the person's worth, even at the expense of ourselves.

This is a definition on relationships in general.

!!! Friendships Matters
* Love one another with brother affection
* Outdo one another in showing honor
* Live in harmony with one another
* Build one another up
* Welcome one another
* Instruct one another
* Greet one another with a holy kiss
* Care for one another
* Serve one another
* Bear one another's burdens

!!! Falling Under Discipleship
Ultimately any relationships between guy girl dynamics should be an attempt to disciple.
The terms boyfriend and girlfriend do communicate something special in that relationship. However that is not necessarily true.

!!! Dating Defined?
The process of getting to know each other in an exclusive manner to increase certainty that marriage would be the most desirable and God glorifying course of action.

Maybe ending the dating relationships would be best. This is not the hard set rule. You are free to disagree.

We would still agree that marriage is somehow in view. So is the idea of exclusivity. That the other person has access to you that other people wouldn't. One is the result of the other. Dating leads to an exclusive relationships to marriage and marriage is an exclusive relationships.

